{"tid":1424652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術討論】其實政權同貨幣係密不可分，貨幣失勢 = 政權失勢","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:43:22.000Z","uid":271829,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33a6a49e57563787ecdf2c93a09c8a7016f4df6c","tid":1424652,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"以前啲貨幣就話有黃金做抵押，<br />\n依家個個國家都喺度印銀紙，百姓相信印出嚟嘅錢，用財產去換該國貨幣，<br />\n係因為信該國政權穩定，日後有能力支付百姓本身應有的財產。<br />\n所以美國嘅強大導致美金廣受承認，而啲弱國為穩定自己貨幣就儲大量強國貨幣如美金。<br />\n轉返轉頭，如果弱國冇曬外匯儲備，咁該國貨幣同財產就同該國政權地位一樣變得垃圾，易受攻擊而貶值。<br />\n而冇曬財富嘅政權亦冇曬力量，容易倒台。<br />\n所以為咗我哋偉大嘅中共，要強力增持人民幣同港紙，千祈千祈唔好依啲冥幣換成美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e80174d1579b9eec328c0d7244a86a315d31ed2","tid":1424652,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"但係伊朗仲未冧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d14179c79db308770583a965e842c7d4c1e5ad","tid":1424652,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"中國有好多美債, 佢要保持人仔唔會眨值, 但香港愈來愈唔穩定就會有外資唔出聲慢慢掟貨.........所以跟成哥風向就冇錯"},{"pid":"cd43f80d95c1438cc09ae80fee49209119f03503","tid":1424652,"uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e80174d1579b9eec328c0d7244a86a315d31ed2","tid":1424652,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"但係伊朗仲未冧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"伊朗嘅貨幣都唔係錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d2b138145b9441f8d593c0837d3504860e0d76","tid":1424652,"uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd43f80d95c1438cc09ae80fee49209119f03503","tid":1424652,"uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e80174d1579b9eec328c0d7244a86a315d31ed2","tid":1424652,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"但係伊朗仲未冧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"伊朗嘅貨幣都唔係錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"伊朗呢啲垃圾國家，本身冇能力制造高端產品，而佢哋貨幣又廢到唔可以買到外國啲產品，<br />\n如果唔係大陸成日偷偷賣武器等高端產品俾佢哋，<br />\n就會好似香港啲警察同老解冇咗槍以上火力嘅武器咁，一早倒咗台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f030d84faab80f14fc03f5025d92ba97e01357","tid":1424652,"uid":292544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e80174d1579b9eec328c0d7244a86a315d31ed2","tid":1424652,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:02.000Z","msg":"但係伊朗仲未冧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"你5會覺得支拿種人真係咁愛國丫嘛 <br />\n真係淨係得香港人搵外國求救？<br />\n愛國只係搵錢既口號 班大陸閪都係打住紅旗反紅旗"},{"pid":"e32c9732867d7e6db02425543053aa614a731ebf","tid":1424652,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"持有冥幣計價嘅資產亦等於間接承認冥幣地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7fd1c366298b55e0c0ab454b73c1be399c1693","tid":1424652,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"個市跌得咁急，都係持美金穩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545561f839aa96856d9d66e17a66cf708709f7ad","tid":1424652,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"所以大家要換美鈔呀"},{"pid":"8baa46048d712175bf0ad3c2ceff3477bc7b498c","tid":1424652,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"mpf又係時候轉去第個穩健嘅市場喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afda76801bb8047d1c3216004683180770b32599","tid":1424652,"uid":286